* [[:en:Istana Luwu|Istana Luwu]]
* [[:en:Istana Maimun|Istana Maimun]]
* [[:en:Istana Merdeka|Istana Merdeka]]
* [[:en:Istana Negara, Jakarta|Istana Negara, Jakarta]]
* [[:en:Istana Wakil Presiden|Istana Wakil Presiden]]
{{column}}
'''Prisons'''
* [[:en:Kambangan Island|Kambangan Island]]
{{column}}
'''Shopping malls'''
* [[List of Indonesia-related topics#Shopping malls in Jakarta|Shopping malls in Jakarta]]
* [[List of Indonesia-related topics#Shopping malls in Bandung|Shopping malls in Bandung]]
* [[List of Indonesia-related topics#Shopping malls in Surabaya|Shopping malls in Surabaya]]
* [[List of Indonesia-related topics#Shopping malls in Batam|Shopping malls in Batam]]
{{column}}
'''Towers'''
* [[:en:Monumen Nasional|Monumen Nasional]]
* [[:en:Wisma 46|Wisma 46]]
{{columns-end}}

